_sText:
Gg_the_office made on request for ]CS[ Scotch Tape by <|TTF|> Jackorito

This map is based after the set of NBC's show The Office. This map isn't an exact replica of the set, but it incorperates some of the layout and features of the set. I incorperated some custom textures, a working elevator, and more. Have fun and enjoy.

Credits goto: ]CS[ Scotch Tape for suggesting the idea, myself for making it, and to all the posters at www.fpsbanana.com for thier wounderful tutorials.

Thanks for downloading!!!
